  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.6">
<l>amuta mamararkaṭ kīnta</l>
<l>nimircuṭa rāḻi neṭumā</l>
<l>lamutilu māṟṟa viṉiya</l>
<l>ṉimirtirai nīḷkaṭa lāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Neṭumāl with a glowing discus he holds up</l>
<l>who gave the ambrosia to the immortals,</l>
<l>he is much sweeter than ambrosia,</l>
<l>the one who is on the large sea with high waves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
